Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:39.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}現実とFight　運命にDive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}ほとばしる情熱(おもい)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}何度息絶えそうでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}ただ真っ直ぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:53.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Don't give up the fight　Time to ignite
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:00.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}この身をかけて　挑む世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:07.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}いっそあるがままに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:12.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}その全てを包み込むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:29.31,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}心中的夢 早已不再只屬於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:35.73,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}掀開那 新的一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:39.90,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}將現實挫敗 把命運主宰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.82,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}滿腔熱誠正澎湃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.37,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}哪怕殘酷到令人窒息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.66,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}也會不離不棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:53.58,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}莫輕易言敗 卷土又重來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:00.63,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}盡全力衝破障礙 向世界宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:07.51,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我願以原本的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:12.35,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}用悲憫之心 包容一切陰霾
